body:
The copilot chat extension provides chat view welcomes:

https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-copilot-chat/blob/146bd7c1492a1eba05003b406fe98cce9398b6d6/package.json#L1596

We need to validate that these still work with the recent refactorings we did.

As a quick test, I tried to add this code to `src/extension/contextKeys/vscode-node/contextKeys.contribution.ts`:

```ts
setTimeout(() => {
	commands.executeCommand('setContext', welcomeViewContextKeys.IndividualDisabled, true);
}, 5000);
```

With the hope that I would see the welcome content, but I did not.
